lead_paragraph: LaShawn Merritt ran the fastest 200 metres in the world this year and Brianna Rollins shocked American record holder Keni Harrison in a world class 100m hurdles final at the U.S. Olympic trials on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Merritt Romps to Fast 200m, Rollins Shocks in Hurdles
